                     <interp inst="t18221023-72-person808" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I made this shift, and am certain the petticoat is part of it.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. It is mine. I never took her shift - I bought it myself.</p>
               <p>
